Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:03.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}Cursed, moving plaster statues...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.38,0:00:05.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}A running anatomy model...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFF&\bord4}A mysterious figure{lit. man ... but it's a woman :P} wearing a white mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:14.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2250)\c&HFFFF&\bord4}We, the Detective Boys, take on the rumors of the Teitan Elementary Mysteries, and find...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.91,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We won’t give in to the hot blazing sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.77,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A gallant and dashing deduction show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:24.12,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The Seven Mysteries of Teitan Elementary!\NUnexplained phenomena turn up everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:25.54,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:27.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:30.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
